  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "荒诞之墙",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "36557721_9_1956-2083",
          "range": "1956-2083",
          "rangeStart": 1956,
          "rangeEnd": 2083,
          "markText": "。只是有一天，突然间就问了个“为什么”，于是，在这份惊讶所掩藏的厌倦中，一切开始了。“开始”，这非常重要。机械生活一系列的行为之后，结局必然就是厌倦，但是，它也开启了意识。它惊醒了意识，然后再继续下去。继续下去，要么是无意识地回到链条上，要么是大彻大悟。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1703167558,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-12-21 22:05:58",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36557721&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1956&rangeEnd=2083",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c51324f0722dd399c51f4c8?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1956&rangeEnd=2083"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "chapterTitle": "荒诞与自杀",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "36557721_7_1980-2056",
          "range": "1980-2056",
          "rangeStart": 1980,
          "rangeEnd": 2056,
          "markText": "愿意去死则意味着我们承认——尽管可能只是本能地承认——这一习惯有多么可笑，承认活着缺乏深层的理由，承认熙熙攘攘的日常生活实在荒谬，承认承受痛苦毫无必要。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1703167504,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-12-21 22:05:04",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36557721&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1980&rangeEnd=2056",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c51324f0722dd399c51f4c8?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1980&rangeEnd=2056"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "36557721_7_1840-1889",
          "range": "1840-1889",
          "rangeStart": 1840,
          "rangeEnd": 1889,
          "markText": "自杀，在某种程度上，就像在情节剧中一般，是一种承认。承认我们被生活超越，或者承认我们没有理解生活。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1703167484,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-12-21 22:04:44",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36557721&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1840&rangeEnd=1889",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c51324f0722dd399c51f4c8?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1840&rangeEnd=1889"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "导读",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "36557721_3_3731-3855",
          "range": "3731-3855",
          "rangeStart": 3731,
          "rangeEnd": 3855,
          "markText": "以前，是要知道生命是否有意义，值得我们活过。而此时，恰恰相反，正是因为生命很可能没有意义，它才值得更好地活过。经历某一种经验，经历命运，就是充分地接受它。但是倘若我们不竭尽全力，充分掌握通过意识显现出来的这份荒诞，就无法经历这我们已知是荒诞的命运。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1703163184,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-12-21 20:53:04",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36557721&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3731&rangeEnd=3855",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c51324f0722dd399c51f4c8?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3731&rangeEnd=3855"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36557721_9_2508-2612",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2508-2612",
      "markText": "明天，就在他原本应该拒绝的时刻，他还期待着明天。这种肉身的反抗，就是荒诞iii。",
      "totalCount": 9570,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36557721&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2508&rangeEnd=2612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c51324f0722dd399c51f4c8?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2508&rangeEnd=2612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36557721_7_903-952",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "903-952",
